Cyberpunk style: A futuristic data courier robot standing in a neon-lit server room, its chest cavity open to reveal streams of glowing JSON data fragments flowing like liquid mercury through transparent tubes. The robot is carefully extracting luminescent data cubes from an ancient, weathered filing cabinet that contrasts sharply with the sleek technological environment. Purple and cyan light reflects off wet metal floors, while holographic view panels float in the air displaying cascading rows of information. Steam rises from cooling vents, and fiber optic cables snake across the ceiling like digital vines. The scene conveys the transformation of old archive systems into modern streaming data.
